有泛民議員提出議案<br />\nsuper majority (47/70): 通過由行政長官提出的政改方案，通過彈劾行政長官，取消議員資格，修改基本法，會期內重提被否決的議案<br />\n<br />\n議員議案最後仍由行政長官決定是否執行，因是行政主導<br />\n另類反DQ:<br />\n根據《基本法》第五十條，若立法會否決《預算案》，行政長官可解散立法會，但須徵詢行政會議的意見，不過假如重選的立法會繼續拒絕通過《預算案》，根據《基本法》第五十二條，行政長官必須辭職。而行政長官在其一任任期內只能解散立法會一次。"},{"pid":"00167884ed4dd3adf7a2a4ee8f51ed60b6499cbf","tid":1392642,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全數否決所有議案，癱瘓整個政府運作 </span></span>"},{"pid":"90fa9917f8355806c0845927946a51ea528c127c","tid":1392642,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:34:02.000Z","msg":"泛民應該會將啲大白象延後<br />\n再將啲痴撚線法例(國歌,社會信用)否決<br />\n再最後提出雙普選(政治問題政治解決,邊個多票邊個有權)"},{"pid":"4514b908a32869379955498969a286c1639b080e","tid":1392642,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:36:50.000Z","msg":"做到咩後話，最重要係民意既表態"},{"pid":"fed09099cc332250b77098378587e5cb53441dfb","tid":1392642,"uid":262091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2abbfddcfaa977b1b127f49a83e245c2696ed4c","tid":1392642,"uid":254961,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T22:24:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光</span>明之子   奮起之<span style=\"color: gold;\">時</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">復</span>赴抗暴    驍勇世<span style=\"color: gold;\">代</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">香</span>城安<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XyZ8fu3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXyZ8fu3.gif&h=3c352850&s={SIZE}\" />夫<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6MuKoo.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6MuKoo.gif&h=c58c6292&s={SIZE}\" />履<span style=\"color: gold;\">革</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">港</span>國兒女   爾汝天<span style=\"color: gold;\">命</span></div></span>"},"citedBy":0,"